reviewText: While I haven't purchased this disc, I wanted to take a moment to comment on one of the seller's other items (which I have purchased): the handmade reproduction of the 'official' Mystic Knights of the Sea building plaque that was both outside the door of the lodge and inside Kingfish's office. This is a gorgeous reproduction that is beautifully made and every fan of the old television show (1951-1953) will appreciate it. Check it out, you won't be sorry.

Another must-have for the serious Amos 'n Andy DVD collector. This episode has only been available since December 2014, so it's not available in previous collections. Picture quality is very good...better than most episodes.
